\v 21 \x + \xo 1:21: \xt Eph 4:17-18.\x*Even though they know \add about\add* \nd GodВҰ105466\nd*, they didn'tВҰ105467 honour or thankВҰ105472 him, butВҰ105479 their theories made them incompetent and their minds turned from perception towards darkness.
