\v 25 as they exchangedВҰ105530 God's truthВҰ105532 for a lie and now worshippedВҰ105539 and served the creation, instead of the creator who \add should be\add* praised throughout the ages. MayВҰ105553 itВҰ105546 be soВҰ105553.
