\v 24 \x + \xo 2:24: \xt Isa 52:5 (LXX).\x*\add Yes,\add* it's been writtenВҰ106068: вҖҳGod's nameВҰ106058 is slanderedВҰ106063 amongВҰ106064 the nations becauseВҰ106061 of youВҰ106062 all.вҖҷ
\p
\v 25 CircumcisionВҰ106069 is of value if you're keeping the law, but if you're breaking the laws, then yourВҰ106083 circumcisionВҰ106082 is just the same as if you're uncircumcisedВҰ106084,
\v 26 so if uncircumcised \add peoples\add* act justly according to the law, even though they're not physically circumcisedВҰ106101, \add God\add* will consider them as hisВҰ106099 people.
