\c 3
\rem /s1 God's Faithfulness; God Remains Faithful
\p
\v 1 SoВҰ106160 what advantage is it in being a Jew and what's the benefitВҰ106168 of circumcisionВҰ106170?
\v 2 A lot in everyВҰ106173 way. FirstlyВҰ106175, Jews were entrustedВҰ106179 with \add the writing down\add* of God's messages.
