\q1 вҖҳYou will be proved right about what you say,
\q2 andВҰ106202 you'll prevail when you're judgedВҰ106225 \add in court\add*.вҖҷ
\p
\v 5 But if ourВҰ106231 sinfulness highlights God's sinlessness, what can weВҰ106236 say about that? \add So\add* isn't God, the one inflictingВҰ106242 the severeВҰ106244 angerВҰ106244, wrong \add to punish us\add*. (Of course this is reasoning from a humanВҰ106247 perspective.)
