\p
\v 7 But if my lie \add exposes\add* God's truthВҰ106263 and so brings him honour, why would he stillВҰ106276 judgeВҰ106280 me as a sinnerВҰ106279?
\v 8 Some people falsely accuse us of saying, вҖҳLet's do evil things so that good might follow.вҖҷ Those who say that deserve theirВҰ106302 punishment.
\s1 No person is guiltless
