\q1
\v 13 \x + \xo 3:13: a \xt Psa 5:9 (LXX); \xo b \xt Psa 140:3.\x*вҖҳTheir words lead to death,
\q2 theirВҰ106360 tonguesВҰ106362 are deceptive.вҖҷ
\q1 вҖҳTheir lipsВҰ106369 spray out poison.вҖҷ
\q1
\v 14 \x + \xo 3:14: \xt Psa 10:7 (LXX).\x*вҖҳTheir mouthsВҰ106373 are full of cursingВҰ106375 andВҰ106376 bitternessВҰ106377.вҖҷ
\q1
\v 15 \x + \xo 3:15-17: \xt Isa 59:7-8.\x*вҖҳThey rush off to go and shed bloodВҰ106384.
\q2
