\v 4 \x + \xo 9:4: \xt Exo 4:22.\x*They're the \add descendants\add* of Yisrael \add (IsraelВҰ109162)\add* who've been adoptedВҰ109165 as \add God's\add* children and \add God revealed \add* his power and the agreements and the Law and the \add temple\add* worship and the promisesВҰ109183.
\v 5 The patriarchs are \add Jewish\add* andВҰ109187 the \nd messiahВҰ109191\nd* who is over everything came from them in a bodyВҰ109196. \add May \+nd GodВҰ109201\+nd* be\add* blessedВҰ109202 throughout the ages. May itВҰ109206 be soВҰ109206.
