\p
\v 1 ThereforeВҰ110066 I'm askingВҰ110065: Did \nd GodВҰ110070\nd* push hisВҰ110075 \add chosen\add* peopleВҰ110073 away? May itВҰ110079 never be, becauseВҰ110081 I also am an IsraeliВҰ110083, a descendant of AbrahamВҰ110087 in the tribeВҰ110088 of Benyamin.\x + \xo 11:1: \xt Php 3:5.\x*
\v 2 \add No,\add* God didn'tВҰ110100 push away hisВҰ110096 peopleВҰ110095 that he knew before \add he chose them\add*. Or don'tВҰ110100 you know what Eliyah wrote when he pleadedВҰ110109 with God to deal with Yisrael:\x + \xo 11:2-3: \xt 1Ki 19:10,14.\x*
