\v 4 But what was the revelationВҰ110139 thatВҰ110149 was given to himВҰ110137:\x + \xo 11:4: \xt 1Ki 19:18.\x* вҖҳI've kept aside sevenВҰ110143 thousandВҰ110143 others who haven't worshipped BaalВҰ110150.вҖҷ
\v 5 SoВҰ110152 too also at the presentВҰ110156 timeВҰ110157, there's a small proportion who've been chosen by \add God's\add* graceВҰ110161.
\v 6 So if it's by grace, then it's no longer by their actions, otherwiseВҰ110171 the grace wouldn't be grace \add at all\add*.
\p
\v 7 What'sВҰ110193 \add the conclusion\add* then? The Israelis didn'tВҰ110199 find what they were lookingВҰ110194 forВҰ110194. Only the chosen ones reaching it and the rest were hardenedВҰ110208
